Filter tab buttons do not use aria‑pressed to indicate which filter is currently active, breaking the accessibility of the tab‑like control.  
  Fix (apply to each button in the map):  
  ```tsx
  <button
    type="button"
    className={[
      'filter-tab-btn',
      activeFilter === tab.value ? 'filter-tab-btn--active' : '',
    ].filter(Boolean).join(' ')}
    tabIndex={activeFilter === tab.value ? 0 : -1}
+   aria-pressed={activeFilter === tab.value}
    onClick={() => onChange(tab.value)}
  >
    {tab.label}
    …
  </button>
  ```

